2.30	Berlin,_Illinois	Berlin, Illinois	Berlin is a village in Sangamon County, Illinois, United States. The population was 140 at the 2000 census. It is part of the Springfield, Illinois Metropolitan Statistical Area. It is also colloquially called "Old Berlin", due to the larger village of New Berlin, Illinois 1.4 miles south.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/23/Illinois_-_background_map.png/256px-Illinois_-_background_map.png
